    (g1 * g2 * g3) • (S3 * S2 * S1) := by
  norm_num [ hA1, hA2, hA3, mul_sub, sub_mul, mul_assoc ] ; ring;
  ext i j ; norm_num ; ring;

/-
The commutator of A1 and A2 is proportional to J2, scaled by the product of gammas and epsilon.
